title: MPPSC MP SET 2025 Apply Online Form
description: MPPSC State Eligibility Test MPSET 2025: Apply Online Form Post Update Date: 27-10-2025 Short Description: MPPSC State Eligibility Test MPSET Exam 2025: Madhya Pradesh Public Service Commission has announced State Eligibility Test SET Exam 2025. Candidates who want to apply online can apply from the link given on Rojgar Result. MPPSC State Eligibility Test Online Form 2025 can be filled from 25 October 2025 to 20 November 2025 .
